{"type":"article_comment","id":355087,"parentType":"article","parentId":18023,"uid":27156,"contents":"<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/item_id-354926#\"><blockquote>言多雅馴，今世難得，惜紀事繁而辨亡少，近傳記，非策論本色也。 </blockquote></a><br>\n蒙先生言。近读史册，略作笔记一二，不敢称策论。拟目如此，亦欲戏拟前世贤文而已。","date":"2020-04-23","agreeCount":0,"discussionCount":0}